# pyenv
#   For a library or package, you might want to ignore these files since the symbols is
#   assigned by the platform. For an app, they can be included.
# .python-version

# pipenv
#   According to pypa/pipenv#1013, pipenv should not be ignore when deploying an application
# Pipfile.lock

# poetry
#   Similar to Pipfile.lock, poetry.lock should be committed when deploying an application
# poetry.lock

# pdm
#   Similar to Pipfile.lock, pdm.lock should be committed when deploying an application
